data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom ranch with hardwood floors throughout. Newer SS appliances in the eat in kitchen. Large sunroom with fireplace and slider doors to large deck and great yard. Full bath with walk in tub and shower. Finished Lower level has a non conforming bedroom and large laundry room plus an additional 3/4 bath and cedar closet. 2 car detached garage and new HVAC in 2015.
